lead_paragraph: The FBI was trying to get a look at thousands of Hillary Clinton's emails on disgraced former congressman Anthony Weiner's computer partly to see if anyone had hacked in to steal classified information, according to court documents unsealed Tuesday.

headline.main: FBI Sought Evidence of Intrusions in Hillary Clinton Emails
headline.print_headline: FBI Sought Evidence of Intrusions in Hillary Clinton Emails
